    {
      "id": "detailed_2_listing_0",
      "firm_id": "detailed_2",
      "description": "Up for sale is a well-maintained vehicle in solid 'good' condition. The engine and transmission run smoothly, and the interior has been kept clean, though you will find some minor wear on the driver's seat bolster and common touchpoints. On the exterior, the paint still holds a nice gloss, but there are a few small stone chips on the hood and a light scuff on the rear bumper from daily use. It is a reliable, honest car that drives great and has plenty of life left for its next owner.",
