    },
    {
      "id": "sybil_4_listing_4",
      "firm_id": "sybil_4",
      "description": "This vehicle is the absolute pinnacle of showroom quality. Meticulously maintained in a climate-controlled garage, the exterior boasts a deep, mirror-like finish entirely free of stone chips, scratches, or swirl marks. The factory paint retains its original luster, complemented by pristine alloy wheels. Step inside to an interior that remains in its original state; the premium leather upholstery shows no signs of creasing or wear, and the cabin still retains that distinctive new-car scent. Every electronic component, from the panoramic sunroof to the high-fidelity surround sound system, operates flawlessly. Mechanically, this car is beyond reproach, having been serviced exclusively by certified technicians with a full, documented history. The engine bay is immaculate, and the ride quality is as smooth and quiet as the day it was first delivered. This is a rare opportunity to own a truly flawless example of automotive excellence. Serious inquiries only.",
